skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my awesome eighties
des: Join your host JC for Awesome 80s, where we dive into the neon glow of a decade that revolutionized music! From synth-pop to glam metal, every song is a journey back to when music was an experience. We celebrate both the iconic hits and hidden gems, bringing the vibrant soundtrack of the 80s to life. Crank up the volume and relive the magic—Awesome 80s is your ultimate time machine to an unforgettable era!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
